@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">

            <div class="card shadow">
                <div class="card-header text-white">
                    <h3 class="mb-0">Privacy Policy</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="card-body">

                    <p>
                        WashWhiz is committed to protecting the privacy and personal information of its users.
                        This system collects basic personal data such as full name, email address, password,
                        and profile images solely for the purpose of account creation, authentication, and
                        providing laundry service features. All information collected is used only within the
                        system to ensure a smooth and personalized user experience.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        We collect and store user-submitted data, including laundry order details such as
                        customer name, service type, weight, and order status. This information is used strictly
                        for managing and tracking laundry services. WashWhiz does not sell, share, or distribute
                        personal data to third parties unless required by law or authorized by the user.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        To maintain data security, WashWhiz implements appropriate measures to protect user
                        information against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. While we strive to
                        use acceptable means to protect personal data, no method of electronic storage or
                        transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and absolute security cannot be guaranteed.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Users are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their account credentials.
                        WashWhiz encourages users to choose strong passwords and avoid sharing login details.
                        In case of suspicious activity, users should update their credentials immediately.
                    </p>

                    <p class="mb-0">
                        By using the WashWhiz system, users agree to the collection and use of information in
                        accordance with this policy. This privacy policy may be updated from time to time to
                        reflect system improvements or changes in data handling practices.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>